                  <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17760417-80-off409 t17760417-80-cd410"></join>.</p>
               <p>The witnesses were examined apart at the request of the prisoner.</p>
               <p>
            
               
                  <persName id="t17760417-80-victim703" type="victimName">
                     SARAH
                      CHILD
                  <interp inst="t17760417-80-victim703" type="surname" value="CHILD"></interp>
